{"tid":996415,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"吞毒蛛與虛幻聲譽","createTime":"2019-01-26T09:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T10:14:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9c402047412fb663b4fba33d688c2e559a75663a","tid":996415,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:21:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190126/20599110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F20599110&d=M3ZqFwR%2B202pwTicjjMYPrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=ec78a7e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190126%2F20599110&h=46f15ad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190126/20599110</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月26日 <br />\n<br />\n吞毒蛛與虛幻聲譽 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190126/large/1548406300_eb4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190126%2Flarge%2F1548406300_eb4d.jpg&h=9adad933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n經常在網上見到反胃及驚嚇片段，都是渴望成名當網紅的YouTuber，拍自虐自殘挑戰極限的「作品」，追求訂閱量、呃like、博讚賞（打賞！）。<br />\n<br />\n很多都無聊又弱智，但肯定吸睛，如生吃毛毛蟲、吞蛆、吞蜥蜴、蛇吻、10,000隻蟑螂洗澡、自製降落傘跳崖（後來死掉）、獸交、鰻魚自慰&hellip;&hellip;看來吃屎是最普通了。<br />\n<br />\n台灣YouTuber「Crazy Man」也真是瘋上腦，把毒蜘蛛送進嘴裏，表演生吞。那渾身毛茸茸，毒牙又駭人的智利紅玫瑰捕鳥蛛（只求出風頭不求甚解的廢青還喚之「利智紅玫瑰捕鳥蛛」──他們也許不知利智是誰？）撩撥一番，此蛛毒性不高但足以毒死一隻鳥，經此挑釁再被朝嘴裏塞，忽地發難，廢青驚呼一聲，吐出血水，原來下唇被咬到，嘴巴很麻，相信離孖膶腸下場不遠。<br />\n<br />\n醫生道，被蜘蛛咬傷，會中毒、感染、皮膚壞死、抽筋、麻痹、休克、影響視力，甚至失明、失去生命&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n或者玩命者有快感，覺得值！這是一個網絡虛幻聲譽操縱個人意志和價值的時代，為了四面八方陌生人點讚，自虐自殘自盡，最後贏得什麼？網民還不是四散另覓新歡？大家揶揄on 9冇藥醫，但既是個人選擇，自負盈虧，又何須同情？  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n護士示威 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n你過什麼年 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"c34329c3cc75dbfad83de72bfa0ea7ed1f543f00","tid":996415,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"想變蜘蛛俠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0be32902217bbe6f7f8e5463cdb2c39744beaa6","tid":996415,"uid":40226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c34329c3cc75dbfad83de72bfa0ea7ed1f543f00","tid":996415,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"想變蜘蛛俠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"咁揀隻勁啲嘅先得啦"}]}